column1: # HelioClim-3 Archive Database of Solar Irradiance v5 (derived from satellite data) and meteorological data (MERRA-2/NASA and GFS/NCEP)

column2: National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) / Goddard Space Flight Center and National Centers for Environmental Prediction (NCEP)

column1: # Meteo Data;MERRA-2 data from 2009-12-31 to 2022-02-28 / GFS data from 2022-03-01 to 2022-03-28
# Date - Instant;The date or instant given for each value corresponds to the end of the summarization
# Take into account the shadows due to relief?;1 (yes
# Irradiation (Wh/m2);Irradiation over the period (-999 if no data)
# Clear-Sky (Wh/m2);Irradiation over the period if the sky were clear
# Top of Atmosphere (Wh/m2);Irradiation over the period at the top of the atmosphere (extraterrestrial)
# Relative humidity (%);Relative humidity at 2 m above ground
# Wind speed (m/s);Wind speed at 10 m above ground
# Wind direction (deg);Wind direction at 10 m above ground (0 means from North
